race.comment: SCULPTOR (2) has transferred from Gary Portelli to Todd Howlett since a desperately close second over 1100m at Goulburn 44 days ago. Nicely drawn and will find this easier than recent assignments. The one to beat. CRAZY MIKKI (4) stuck to the task impressively when resuming over this course and distance last time out. Fitter for that run and should hold the same level of performance. CALEDONIAN (3) is back from a 19-week spell. Trialled well here on 11 October so although she hasn't fired in two previous first-up runs she looks forward enough to run well here. SNATCHREILLY (1) is back from a 24-week break. Good fresh performer who raced well in similar races to this under big weights last prep. Should be in the finish. MAGNOLIA JEWEL (6) goes fast and should be prominent for a long way.
